<h1 class="mb-5">Blog</h1>
<p>I'm not the best story teller in the world if I'm honest, but I've given it a go by writing some blog
        posts.</p>
<div class="my-5">
        <ul class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
                {%- for post in collections.post -%}
                <li class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute filter -inset-0.5 opacity-75 blur-md bg-gradient-to-r from-{{post.data.from}}-600 to-{{post.data.to}}-600 rounded-lg"></div>
                        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="relative flex justify-center items-center bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-8 cursor-pointer text-center font-medium dark:bg-white dark:text-gray-900">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </li>
                {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
</div>